Class TextFormattedIntermediateResponseAccessLogMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.unboundid.ldap.sdk.unboundidds.logs.v2.text.TextFormattedLogMessage
      • com.unboundid.ldap.sdk.unboundidds.logs.v2.text.TextFormattedAccessLogMessage

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AccessLogMessage, IntermediateResponseAccessLogMessage, LogMessage, OperationRequestAccessLogMessage, java.io.Serializable

    @NotMutable
@ThreadSafety(level=INTERFACE_THREADSAFE)
public final class TextFormattedIntermediateResponseAccessLogMessage
extends TextFormattedRequestAccessLogMessage
implements IntermediateResponseAccessLogMessage
    This class provides a data structure that holds information about a text-formatted operation request access log message.
    NOTE: This class, and other classes within the com.unboundid.ldap.sdk.unboundidds package structure, are only supported for use against Ping Identity, UnboundID, and Nokia/Alcatel-Lucent 8661 server products. These classes provide support for proprietary functionality or for external specifications that are not considered stable or mature enough to be guaranteed to work in an interoperable way with other types of LDAP servers.
